<Content>I was looking at getting a less expensive mp3 player to use in the gym.  After reading the reviews for all of the different options, I decided on the Sandisk Clip because it received the best reviews.  I'm not disappointed at all with my decision.  I use it more than I thought I would.  It's a great little product if you don't feel like dropping $150+ on an I-Pod.  
