<Content>I finally have the perfect mp3 player!!! I bought my wife the Red 2GB Sandisk Clip for Christmas, and after checking it out, I went out the next day and bought myself one too (Black 2GB model). It's an awesome mp3 player for a great price with a ton of features and it looks good with easy functionality.   Easily the best entry level and compact mp3 player out there!!! You won't be disappointed!!!!!!     
