<Content>My last MP3 player was a 256MB iRiver with an FM tuner.  This MP3 player is a MAJOR upgrade for me.  On top of the obvious upgrade in memory, this player has an easier to navigate display and far superior sound quality.  The synch with Windows XP is super easy.  I'm a BIG fan of this MP3 player.  
